<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Password Reset</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Hello,</h2>
    <p>Your account has been successfully created. Please find your initial login credentials below:</p>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
    <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <%= tempPassword %></p>
    <p>
        For security reasons, please reset your password as soon as possible. Click the link below to set a new password:
        <a href="<%= link %>">Reset Your Password</a>
    </p>
    <p>If you did not request this, please contact support immediately.</p>
    <p>Thank you!</p>
</body>
</html>
